/td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/usoneldarblackrose.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Soneldar Blackrose</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 58<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(12/2/01 1:03:31 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm9.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=111.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Anarchy Online free month to former players</span><hr size=1> Also, Funcom had the balls to start up on another game just as AO was doomed to failure by all gaming magazines... hmm, I smell a rat. <p>Soneldar Blackrose<br><b>Half Elven Lightbearer of the First Fist of Light</b><br>Ambassador, Head of Translation<br><i>"You have insulted my love, myself, and my family... and now you shall pay."</i><br>Soneldar Blackrose to Shintou Shinai<br><i>"Fear me o daemon, for I am the Blackrose!  I shall be the wings that carry you to your death!"</i><br>-Warcry of the Blackrose</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ueliezeroferudin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Eliezer of Erudin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 257<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(12/3/01 3:45:32 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm9.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=111.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Anarchy Online free month to former players</span><hr size=1> I got the email.  It is not enough to get me to play the game.<br><br>The idea of a Sci-Fi game interested me, but what they offered was just 'Magic' masquerading as Technology.  The whole Nano thing grated on me, and I found them too annoying.  If I want to have a zillion buffs, I'll play a Shaman on EQ.<br><br>All I wanted was a Character not laden down with a zillion spells...er Nano Formula.  Not possible. :-p <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ubjond.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Bjond</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_redspot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 14<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(12/11/01 5:28:07 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm9.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=111.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Anarchy Online free month to former players</span><hr size=1> AO has truly stunning graphics.  If all you want is nice visuals, that's the game for you.  I bailed out due to lack of bug fixing.  It's still horrible -- every patch adds more than it fixes and they still ignore test server reports and patch the bugs in anyway.<br><br>Oh, and the lead designer posted his intent to start a nerf-pogrom.  Not in so many words, but that's what it amounted to.  He'll get his way eventually.  I just can't see spending time on a character that will be trashed by the game company.<br><br>If it survives, AO will be a really nice game about 2 or 3 years from now. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm9.showPrevMessage?topicID=111.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm9.showNextMessage?topicID=111.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm9.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=111.topic&index=3><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table